18:59.000 --> 19:02.000
What is it? Loyalty Addition

19:02.000 --> 19:11.000
La is a type of non-guaranteed bonus declared by LIC for certain plans that have completed a minimum number of years.

19:11.000 --> 19:21.000
It is paid only once at the time of maturity or death and is a reward for staying invested in the policy for a longer duration.

19:21.000 --> 19:23.000
