27. Guaranteed Addition

20:04.000 --> 20:13.000
What is it? Guaranteed Additions are fixed bonuses declared in advance by LIC in select plans.

20:13.000 --> 20:21.000
Unlike Reversionary or Loyalty bonuses, Gaz are assured and mentioned in the plan brochure itself.

