20:51.000 --> 20:55.000
28. Next Last Near Birthday

20:55.000 --> 21:07.000
What is it? In LIC policies, your age is used for premium calculation but how its calculated depends on whether the plan uses last birthday,

21:07.000 --> 21:16.000
next birthday or nearest birthday. Last birthday, your age as of your last birthday.

21:16.000 --> 21:21.000
Next birthday, your age on your upcoming birthday.

21:21.000 --> 21:25.000
nearest birthday, the age you are closest to.

21:25.000 --> 21:31.000
